angular cli
  - npm i -g @angular/cli
create project
  ng new "name of my project"

what it angular.json
  this file We can modific our project, is like webpack.js 

tseslint.json
  this file help us to write code of the best way and clear

karma testing

Angular can run in many environments 
  platFormBrowserDynamic() 
    angular or my app is running in the browser
    this is my webpApp

app.module.ts
  We'll register all our components to use in all our template

decorationClass 
  import {Component} 'angular-core'
  ejemplo :
    @Component({
      selector:'app-component',
      template: 'h1--h1',
      templateUrl:'app.component.html'
      styleUrl: 'styles.css',
    })

HOW CAN I CREATE COMPONENTS AUTOMATIC?
  you just must run command
  -ng generate component urlpath
  -ng g c file/components/header

directives 
  *ngIf  <p *ngIf="show" > hola </p>
  *ngFor  <li *ngFor="let item of names; let i = index"> {{index}}: {{item}} </li>
          if you need to use item in some attribute:
          <p [id]="item.name">{{item.name}}</p>
  -events 
    (click)="myFunction()"
    ng-click="myFunction()"

router 
 [routerLink]="['home','hola','id']" is home/hola/id

services
  give information who need it
  make request CRUD(create, delete, put)
  keepts persistent ny data